# Phase 2 A/B Test Results Analysis - "Chop Survival" Attempt

## Test Parameters
- **Duration:** ~13.5 hours (2026-02-03 - 2026-02-04)
- **Focus:** Testing "Chop Survival" Hybrids vs Baseline
- **Market Conditions:** Difficult/Choppy

